trans-unit.source: Provides a drop shadow for display by <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner"></xref> classes.
trans-unit.target: Ger en bakgrundsskugga för visning av <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner"> </xref> klasser.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] A <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner> displays a ShadowGlyph if the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeDesignerTheme.ShowDropShadow%2A> property is set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]En <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner>visar en ShadowGlyph om den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeDesignerTheme.ShowDropShadow%2A>egenskap är inställd på `true`.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeDesignerTheme.ShowDropShadow%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ShadowGlyph"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ShadowGlyph"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Returns the bounds for the glyph on the specified <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar det giltiga intervallet för tecknet på den angivna <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner"></xref> with which the glyph is associated.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner"> </xref> med vilket tecknet är associerade.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to indicate whether the glyph appears on the activity designer surface; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>som anger om tecknet finns på aktiviteten designytan; Annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Rectangle"></xref> that represents the bounds for the glyph.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Rectangle"> </xref> som representerar det giltiga intervallet för tecknet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the priority setting for the glyph on the activity designer surface.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar prioritetsinställningen för tecknet på aktiviteten designytan.

trans-unit.source: An integer value that represents the priority setting for the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ShadowGlyph"></xref> on the activity designer surface.
trans-unit.target: Ett heltalsvärde som representerar prioritetsinställningen för den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ShadowGlyph"> </xref> på aktiviteten designytan.
